SUMMARY:You (probably) Haven't Seen This Before with IULMIA
DESCRIPTION:For the past four years\, the IU Libraries Moving Image Archi
 ve has hosted a regular screening series showcasing rare archival shorts 
 that highlight underrepresented narratives and experimental motion-pictur
 e practicesâ€”works that expand the very idea of "cinema."On Thursday\, M
 arch 26th at 5:30 p.m.\, the BFCA and IULMIA will present a collaborative
  edition of You (probably) Haven't Seen This Before\, curated by Publicat
 ions &amp\; Programming Associate Essence London. The event will be held 
 in IULMIA's Screening Room and will last under an hour! Refreshments will
  be served following the screening.
